    <item>
      <title>美元波动，澳元因加息前景而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firms-near-3-month-high-rate-cut-bets-dwindle-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期美联储今年不太可能大幅降息，美元在三个月高点附近波动，而在央行表示不排除再次加息后，澳元上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firms-near-3-month-high-rate-cut-bets-dwindle-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 01:47:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
